Bug Report
===========


Summary:
An error message was not displayed when the 'Message' field was left empty in the 'Contact Us' form.

Description:
The 'Contact Us' form allowed submission without displaying an error message, despite the 'Message' field being required.

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Navigate to the 'Contact Us' page.
2. Fill out the form with valid inputs in all fields except the 'Message' field.
3. Submit the form.

Expected Result:
An error message should be displayed, indicating that the 'Message' field is required.

Actual Result:
No error message was displayed.

Severity: Medium  
Priority: High  

Environment:
- Browser: Chrome 117.0  
- OS: Windows 11  
- URL: https://www.tendable.com/contact-us  


